des: Each week, Restaurant Authority curates and vettes, what they believe are the top ten restaurants in the US, based on a a mix of quality, dining experience, online reputation, culinary innovation, relevance and a good old fashioned taste test. Updated weekly, the a new top ten comes out every monday.
